”’Щ@5a9283e18af06a8f4226f148c783159db8aa5d6b66b79e2611fb9af577a0094cЪ	%Title: This week in Nushell #270
Path: Nushell
Content:
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14165] added 
``command_type``
 to help
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14159] added 
``name``
 to 
``$env.config.keybindings``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14158] made adding newlines with 
``to text``
 more consistent and opt-out-able
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14146] updated reedline
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14141] added metadata on 
``open --raw``
 with bytestreams
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14140] tried to fix osc633 escaping yet again
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14127] added 
``start_time``
 to 
``ps -l``
 on macos
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14125] added is_const to 
``help commands``
 and 
``scope commands``
sholderbach 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14161] bumped 
``brotli``
 to 6.0.0
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14138] made the contributor image wider
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14136] bumped the version to 0.99.2
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14128] added slice as a search term on 
``range``
ayax79 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14148] upgraded to polars 0.43
hustcer 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14131] added a GitHub action to CI to add milestones automatically
sgvictorino 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14118] fixed a bug when exporting constants with type signatures in modules
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14095] added a error when closure param lists aren't terminated by 
``|``
PhotonBursted 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14096] implemented defensive handling of errors when transposing
adaschma 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14073] let 
``url build_query``
 accept records with lists of strings
zhiburt 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14070] introduced footer_inheritance option to table rendering
Kither12 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14035] fixed a panic if tokens are placed after a redirection
JoaquinTrinanes 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14011] fixed a bug in 
``range contains``
